Im unsure about haste stacking.<br>
I know its one haste item and one haste spell.<br>
But what about the Epic. Its &quot;song&quot; haste right?<br>
So lets say i have a haste item like FBSS and Epic.<br>
Would mean i have about 61% haste on.<br>
But what about chanter spells like Speed of the Shissar?<br>
It will &quot;only&quot; give the 21% from FBSS and the 66% of the spell right? Epic will just add the stats not the haste in that case cause Shissar is the better haste spell.<br>
<br>
Am i correct? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Im unsure because some high lvl monk told me otherwise and i want to prove that im right.<br>
<br>
